ssive%20competition%20from%20other%20apps%2C%20especially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchart-how-instagram-could-benefit-tiktok-ban-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTikTok%20is%20still%20bigger%20than%20either%20Facebook%20or%20Instagram%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20testified.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20like%20it%20when%20our%20competitors%20do%20better%20than%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he's%20determined%20to%20grow%20Meta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20sort%20of%20bet%20that%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20rest%20until%20we%20are%20doing%20quite%20a%20bit%20better%20than%20we%20are%20doing%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Zuckerberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22546ba0ef-dea4-4824-b394-a47b73d68e35%5C%22%3EFacebook%20Camera%20app%20struggles%20were%20a%20source%20of%20worry%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInstagram's%20early%20rise%20shook%20Zuckerberg.%20As%20his%20company%20struggled%20to%20mount%20its%20response%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-camera-app-screenshots-2012-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%20Camera%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20CEO%20began%20to%20lose%20his%20patience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20going%20on%20with%20our%20photos%20team%3F%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20wrote%20in%20a%202011%20message%20to%20top%20executives%2C%20as%20revealed%20by%20the%20FTC%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZuckerberg%20then%20described%20a%20number%20of%20individuals%2C%20whose%20names%20were%20redacted%2C%20as%20being%20%26quot%3Bchecked%20out.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20another%20person%20didn't%20want%20%26quot%3Bto%20work%20with%20this%20team%20because%20he%20thinks%20this%20team%20sucks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Zuckerberg%20downplayed%20his%20concern%20about%20Instagram.%20He%20said%20the%20photo-sharing%20app%20was%20%26quot%3Badjacent%26quot%3B%20to%20what%20Facebook%20was%20trying%20to%20