0with%20company%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20found%20him%20fairly%20impressive%20although%20disappointingly%20(or%20maybe%20positive%20for%20us)%20unambitious%2C%26quot%3B%20Zuckerberg%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20colleagues%20after%20the%20meeting%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20at%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJan%20Koum%20and%20Brian%20Acton%20cofounded%20WhatsApp%20in%202009.%20Zuckerberg%20said%20in%20his%20testimony%20that%20he%20thinks%20he%20was%20referring%20to%20Koum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20his%20email%2C%20Zuckerberg%20seemed%20uneasy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20Koum%20was%20clearly%20smart%20but%20that%20he%20and%20Acton%20were%20staunchly%20opposed%20to%20growing%20their%20messaging%20app%20enough%20to%20be%20a%20real%20threat%20to%20Facebook.%20Zuckerberg%20would%20go%20on%20to%20buy%20WhatsApp%20in%202014%20for%20%2419%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-antitrust-trial-testimony-hours-witness-stand-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744881722000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66296d6523b29110d302b6bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-antitrust-trial-testimony-hours-witness-stand-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meta%20CEO%20and%20founder%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20spent%20more%20than%2010%20hours%20on%20the%20witness%20stand%20in%20the%20social%20media%20empire's%20landmark%20antitrust%20trial.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nmusumeci%40businessinsider.com%20(Natalie%20Musumeci%2CBrent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A70%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-antitrust-trial-testimony-hours-witness-stand-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20acted%20for%20free%20in%20M