ot-vincent-donofrio-charlie-cox-marvel-return-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVincent%20D'Onofrio%3C%2Fa%3E)%20who%20has%20crawled%20his%20way%20out%20of%20prison%20and%20has%20been%20elected%20as%20the%20city's%20mayor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20the%20credits%20roll%2C%20Fisk%20has%20completely%20taken%20control%20of%20New%20York%20by%20enacting%20martial%20law%20and%20declaring%20vigilantism%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20ending%20explained%2C%20and%20what%20to%20know%20about%20%26quot%3BDaredevil%3A%20Born%20Again%26quot%3B%20season%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWarning%3A%20Spoilers%20ahead.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c1ddd566-20fe-4ca3-9fed-1aadb5e7d168%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWilson%20Fisk%20crushes%20the%20head%20of%20the%20police%20commissioner%20with%20his%20bare%20hands%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221935%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20large%20bald%20man%20wears%20a%20white%20suit%20with%20a%20light%20blue%20striped%20shirt.%20He's%20wiping%20his%20face%20with%20a%20napkin%20and%20his%20hand%20is%20covered%20in%20blood.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ff9c4ec6ad288d147e458e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221209%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKingpin%20murdered%20Police%20Commissioner%20Gallo%20with%20his%20bare%20hands%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BDaredevil%3A%20Born%20Again%26quot%3B%20finale.%3Cp%3EMarvel%20Television%2FDisney%2B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20season%20has%20revolved%20around%20a%20few%20key%20mysteries%2C%20most%20notably%3A%20Why%20did%20Bullseye%20(Wilson%20Bethel)%20kill%20Murdock's%20best%20friend%2C%20Foggy%20Nelson%20(Elden%20Henson)%2C%20in%20the%20first%20episode%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20finale%20explains%20that%20Vanessa%20Fisk%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdaredevil-born-again-ayelet-zurer-vanessa-kingpin-took-over-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAyelet%20Zurer%3C%2Fa%3E)%20hired%20him%20to%20do%20it%20in%20order%20to%20cover%20up%20the%20fact%20that%20she%20was%20using%20a%20centuries-old%20charter%20that%20would%20let%20Kingpin%20use%20Red%20Hook%20as%20a%20freeport%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20let%20them%20launder%20money%20legally%2C%20and%20run%20the%20area%20as%20they%20wish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECombined%20with%20Kingpin's%20Anti-Vigilante%20Task%20Force%2C%20this%20is%20part%20of%20the%20villain's%20grand%20plan%20to%20turn%20New%20York%20into%20a%20totalitarian%20police%20state%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20exactly%20what%20happens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDaredevil%20goes%20on%20the%20run%20as%20vigilantes%20are%20outlawed%2C%20and%20Frank%20Castle%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjon-bernthal-punisher-return-daredevil-born-again-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJon%20Bernthal%3C%2Fa%3E)%20is%20locked%20up%20in%20Kingpin's%20murky%20underground%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKingpin%20takes%20things%20a%20step%20further%20and%20kills%20Police%20Commissioner%20Gallo%20(Michael%20Gaston)%20by%20crushing%20his%20head%20with%20his%20bare%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20Marvel's%20goriest%20moment%20yet%2C%20as%20Gallo's%20forehead%20caves%20inwards%2C%20and%20his%20jaw%20comes%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20violent%20scene%20dispels%20any%20doubts%20about%20Disney's%20commitment%20to%20continuing%20the%20Netflix%20show's%20brutal%20streak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20season%20finale%20ends%20with%20Daredevil%20starting%20to%20form%20a%20rebellion%20in%20Josie's%20Bar%2C%20with%20a%20few%20remaining%20NYPD%20officers%20who%20aren't%20on%20Fisk's%20payroll.%20Hopefully%2C%20he'll%20recruit%20a%20few%20superheroes%20to%20the%20cause%20in%20%26quot%3BDaredevil%3A%20Born%20Again%26quot%3B%20season%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e1db0cbd-de67-4014-95de-9c77ddcdcbf7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BDaredevil%3A%20Born%20Again%26quot%3B%20season%20two%20is%20in%20production%2C%20and%20Matt%20Murdock's%20got%20a%20brand%20new%20look.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20in%20a%20black%20tactical%20superhero%20suit%20crouching%20in%20front%20of%20a%20humvee.%20His%20costume%20has%20red%20lenses%20and%20horns%20on%20the%20mask.%20On%20his%20chest%20is%20a%20'DD'%20logo%20in%20red.%20Stood%20next%20two%20him%20are%20two%20police%20officers%20with%20%26quot%3BAVTF%26quot%3B%20branding%20on%20their%20bulletproof%20vests.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ff9f70a466d2b74ab34857%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222369%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECharlie%20Cox%20wearing%20the%20black%20Daredevil%20suit%20on%20set%20in%20New%20York.%3Cp%3EJose%20Perez%2FBauer-Griffin%2FGC%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20clear%20when%20%26quot%3BDaredevil%3A%20Born%20Again%26quot%3B%20season%20two%20will%20be%20released%20on%20Disney%2B%2C%20but%20Marvel%20fans%20should%20be%20safe%20in%20the%20knowledge%20that%20the%20cast%20and%20crew%20have%20been%20filming%20the%20next%20batch%20of%20episodes%20since%20February%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20production%20goes%20smoothly%2C%20then%20the%20show%20could%20arrive%20in%20early%202026%20%E2%80%94%20perhaps%20at%20a%20similar%20time%20to%20the%20first%20season's%20March%20release%20date%2C%20depending%20on%20how%20long%20post-production%20takes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20much%20is%20known%20about%20the%20exact%20plot%20of%20%26quot%3BDaredevil%3A%20Born%20Again%26quot%3B%20season%20two%2C%20but%20it%20will%20likely%20see%20Murdock%20and%20Karen%20Page%20(Deborah%20Ann%20Woll)%20rebelling%20against%20Kingpin%20and%20officially%20forming%20the%20army%20they%20mentioned%20in%20the%20closing%20moments%20of%20the%20first%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20all%20of%20the%20main%20cast%2C%20including%20Cox%2C%20D'Onofrio%2C%20Bethel%2C%20and%20Zurer%2C%20are%20expected%20