that%20no%20one%20would%20likely%20open%20a%20door%20for%20him%20unless%20they%20first%20felt%20comfortable%20with%20him.%20He%20reworked%20his%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20to%20reflect%20his%20authentic%20personality.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhobbies-look-great-on-resume-2017-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHe%20added%20an%20'Interests'%20section%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20placed%20it%20at%20the%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20made%20sense%20to%20me%20because%20when%20I'd%20first%20meet%20someone%2C%20I'd%20share%20some%20unique%20tidbits%20about%20myself%20to%20build%20a%20warm%20first%20impression%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20went%20beyond%20listing%20generic%20interests%20and%20strove%20to%20highlight%20specific%20details%20that%20couldn't%20be%20associated%20with%20anyone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20saying%20things%20like%20'I%20enjoy%20cooking%2C'%20I%20shared%20that%20I%20entered%20a%20pie%20contest%20and%20came%20in%203rd%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20small%2C%20quirky%20detail%20made%20me%20stick%20out%20and%20made%20me%20human.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22410121ed-b85e-4867-a828-c662a316ee1b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Including%20tech%20phrases%20and%20terminology%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnderson%20realized%20he%20needed%20to%20be%20able%20to%20speak%20the%20industry%20lingo%20he%20used%20in%20his%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20confidently.%20While%20the%20writer%20he'd%20hired%20had%20filled%20his%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20with%20all%20the%20right%20buzzwords%20for%20the%20tech%20industry%2C%20it%20created%20a%20new%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20actually%20talk%20about%20my%20experience%20in%20the%20language%20of%20the%20tech%20world%20during%20phone%20screens%2C%26quot%3B%20Anderson%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20caused%20me%20to%20stall%20in%20the%20interview%20process%20because%20I%20sounded%20