0the%20city%20applauds%20Rahul%20on%20this%20stroke%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F316563%2Ftamil-nadu-sustsainable-home-with-plastic-bottles-and-mud-chuzi-vinu-daniel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earchitectural%20brilliance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20particular%20call%20will%20stay%20etched%20in%20his%20mind.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20dad%20phoned%20me%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CRahul%2C%20what%20have%20you%20done%3F%20Wherever%20I%20go%2C%20they%20talk%20about%20the%20walkway.%20Everybody%20is%20saying%20how%20lovely%20it%20is.%20I%20think%20your%20idea%20was%20excellent.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fmalabar-hill-walkway-1_11zon-1744813689.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20nature%20trail%20is%20made%20of%20wood%20and%20supported%20by%20steel%2C%20sustainability%20is%20in%20the%20details%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fmalabar-hill-walkway-1_11zon-1744813689.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fmalabar-hill-walkway-1_11zon-1744813689-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fmalabar-hill-walkway-1_11zon-1744813689-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fmalabar-hill-walkway-1_11zon-1744813689-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fmalabar-hill-walkway-1_11zon-1744813689-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-420971%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20nature%20trail%20is%20made%20of%20wood%20and%20supported%20by%20steel%3B%20sustainability%20is%20in%20the%20details%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20walk%20the%20walkway%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20see%20what%20Iftikhar%20meant.%20The%20structure%20is%20an%20aesthetic%20argument%20for%20how%20beauty%20does%20not%20have%20to%20come%20at%20a%20cost%20to%20nature.%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20proclivity%20towards%20designing%2C%20keeping%20nature%20in%20mind%2C%20stems%20from%20his%20childhood%2C%20which%20was%20marked%20by%20a%20rendezvous%20with%20the%20natural%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20went%20to%20boarding%20school%20in%20Nainital%20at%20the%20age%20of%20eight.%20Sherwood%20College%20is%20up%20the%20foothills%20of%20the%20Himalayas.%20There%20were%20forests%20all%20around%20us.%20From%20our%20playfields%2C%20we%20could%20actually%20walk%20into%20the%20forest.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20were%20to%20venture%20into%20the%20forest%2C%20you%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20Rahul%20playing.%20Instead%2C%20you%E2%80%99d%20see%20him%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F415182%2Ftrekking-with-kids-beginner-friendly-trails-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexploring%20the%20wilderness%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Around%20the%2019th%20century%2C%20the%20Malabar%20area%20in%20Mumbai%20shared%20ground%20with%20hyenas%20and%20jackals.%C2%A0With%20time%2C%20buildings%20and%20skyscrapers%20dotted%20its%20skyline%2C%20and%20what%20remained%20of%20the%20jungle%20was%20a%2012-acre%20microbiome%20where%20rose-ringed%20parakeet%2C%20coppersmith%20barbet%2C%20and%20golden%20oriole%20continue%20to%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Rahul%20walks%20along%20the%20nature%20trail%2C%20a%20d%C3%A9j%C3%A0%20vu%20creeps%20up%20on%20him.%20He%20recalls%20venturing%20into%20the%20Malabar%20Forest%20when%20he%20was%20around%2011%20years%20old%20with%20his%20dog%2C%20walking%2C%20exploring%2C%20and%20wondering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20never%20afraid%20of%20being%20in%20the%20forest%20by%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20known%20to%20find%20pathways%2C%20to%20intuitively%20know%20the%20way.%E2%80%9D%20He%20did%20not%20need%20a%20GPS%2C%20he%20was%20guided%20by%20the%20rhythms%20of%20nature.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20design%20philosophy%20backed%20by%20sustainable%20sensibilities%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDesign%20viability%20and%20beautiful%20views%20convene%20in%20the%20nature%20trail%3B%20its%20Sea%20Viewing%20Deck%20offering%20the%20average%20visitor%20a%20chance%20to%20see%20their%20city%20through%20a%20new%20lens.%20Through%20the%20482%20metres%20it%20covers%2C%20the%20walkway%20embodies%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20vision%20for%20nature%20to%20become%20a%20centrepiece%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F419684%2Fsustainable-architecture-in-india-using-stone-lime-moss-the-timber-residence-vagator%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublic%20architecture%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elevated%20walkway%20begins%20on%20Siri%20Road%20behind%20the%20Kamala%20Nehru%20Park%20and%20ends%20in%20the%20verdant%20sprawl%20of%20the%20Doongerwadi%20Woods.%20Segueing%20into%20the%20conversation%20of%20how%20the%20project%20saw%20the%20light%20of%20day%2C%20Rahul%20backtracks%20to%20one%20of%20his%20walks%20through%20this%20stretch%20during%20the%20COVID-19-induced%20lockdown%2C%20when%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20were%20exploring%20the%20neighbourhood.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%20I%20climbed%20over%20the%20fence.%20That%20was%20the%20day%20it%20all%20began%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20What%20followed%20were%20weeks%20of%20%E2%80%9Creading%20the%20site%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20in%20understanding%20how%20the%20sit