s%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vasanthi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20the%20nearest%20hospital%20is%2040%20km%20away%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedical%20emergencies%20in%20a%20remote%20village%20come%20with%20real%20risks.%20%E2%80%9CRecently%2C%20a%20friend%20lost%20her%20husband%20because%20of%20not%20being%20able%20to%20access%20medical%20help%20in%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anurag.%20%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20small%20primary%20care%20hospital%20run%20by%20an%20NGO%2010%20kilometres%20away.%20But%20for%20proper%20treatment%2C%20you%20have%20to%20go%20to%20Almora%20or%20Haldwani.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20improve%20response%20times%2C%20the%20couple%20is%20helping%20set%20up%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20and%20database%20of%20local%20ambulances%2C%20doctors%2C%20and%20taxi%20drivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForest%20fires%20are%20another%20concern.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20somebody%20spots%20a%20fire%2C%20they%20call%20neighbours%20to%20help%20out.%20A%20prompt%20community%20response%20is%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiving%20close%20to%20nature%20has%20made%20the%20couple%20deeply%20conscious%20of%20their%20footprint.%20They%20compost%20wet%20waste%2C%20burn%20paper%20and%20cardboard%20in%20the%20fireplace%2C%20and%20reuse%20disposable%20items%20%E2%80%94%20like%20turning%20plastic%20cups%20into%20planters%20and%20glass%20bottles%20into%20decorative%20installations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20club%20store%20runs%2C%20carpool%20with%20neighbours%2C%20and%20grow%20what%20we%20can%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vasanthi.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20not%20only%20helps%20us%20reduce%20waste%20but%20also%20cuts%20down%20our%20carbon%20footprint.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcompost-and-growing-veggies_11zon-1744541099.jpg%5C%22%20width